OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLight winds,
OL,6,Fwith low cloud and coastal mist again
OL,7,Fspilling inland from the North Sea.
OL,8,FBest of the clear spells will be out
OL,9,Ftowards the west. Staying dry
OL,10,Fthroughout.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA similar day to Thursday,
OL,13,Fwith cloud clearing through the
OL,14,Fmorning, to give good sunny spells.
OL,15,FLikely feeling cooler due to a fresher
OL,16,Fnorth to northeasterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
