OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,6,Ffine and largely dry, with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Skies remaining clearer
OL,8,Fovernight, with winds more generally
OL,9,Ffrom the north, perhaps brisk along
OL,10,Fcoasts on Saturday. Temperatures near
OL,11,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
